"""
Oracle Static Log Collection Monitoring Script
-----------------------------------------------
Checks which Oracle DB hosts are sending logs to Splunk (via Elasticsearch),
compares against an internal referential, and generates a CSV/Excel report
sent by email and stored in PostgreSQL.

HOW TO ADD A NEW REGION:
    1. Add the region key to list_oracle_static in lst_static.py
    2. That's it — no changes needed in this script.
"""

